Skills.Name: Flying Adder
Skills.Description: Lowers ATK of single enemy with highest ATK by <color=red>{0}%</color> for 15s. Inflicts <color=red>{1}%</color> DMG on all enemies within 150 cm of target enemy. Further inflicts Knockback by {2} cm.
Skills.ShortDescription: Lowers ATK of single enemy. Inflicts DMG and Knockback on all enemies within range

Skills.Name: Knock Down
Skills.Description: Raises ATK of all Elf allies by <color=red>{0}%</color> for 15s. Also raises Speed by <color=red>{1}%</color> for 15s. Further shields DMG (<color=red>{2}%</color> of skill user's ATK) for 15s if Red Elemental.
Skills.ShortDescription: Raises ATK and Speed of all Elf allies, shields DMG if Red Elemental

Skills.Name: Cloudless Rain
Skills.Description: Lowers DEF of all enemies by <color=red>{0}%</color> for 10s. Further inflicts 3-hit DMG ({1}% + {2}% + {3}%).
Skills.ShortDescription: Lowers DEF, inflicts 3-hit DMG on all enemies

Skills.Name: Strike Combo
Skills.Description: Inflicts <color=red>75.00%-1500.00%</color> DMG according to Combo Bonus.

Skills.Name: Glimmering Blade
Skills.Description: Every 15s after start of Wave, raises DMG Inflicted for all allies by <color=red>{1}%</color> multiplied by number of Red Elementals in party for 15s. Further recovers SP by <color=red>{3}</color> if Elf.
Skills.ShortDescription: Every 15s after start of Wave, raises DMG Inflicted for all allies based on number of Red Elementals in party, recovers SP if Elf
